&lt;p&gt;🌏 &lt;strong&gt;Mission:&lt;/strong&gt; At Too Good To Go, we have an ambitious mission: to inspire and empower everyone to fight food waste together. More than 1/3 of all food produced in the world is wasted, which has a huge impact on our planet - 10% of greenhouse gas emissions, to be exact.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
