&lt;p&gt;As a marketplace, many of our most critical challenges revolve around &lt;strong&gt;supply-demand dynamics, user behaviour, and marketplace efficiency&lt;/strong&gt;. Your team works on problems such as &lt;strong&gt;personalisation, pricing, optimisation, and forecasting&lt;/strong&gt;, helping us move from reactive analysis to proactive, model-driven systems.&lt;/p&gt;
