&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strengthen the DS↔ML handoff&lt;/strong&gt;, ensuring models move from prototype to production reliably and that the two disciplines collaborate closely from the start of each initiative&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partner with Product and business leaders&lt;/strong&gt; to identify high-impact opportunities where data science and ML can drive step-change improvements, and translate them into a focused team roadmap&lt;/li&gt;
